As a child I want boxes so that I can store shoes for Polly pockets.

As a parent I want boxes so that I can store junk mail.

As an artist I want an engraved box so that I can paint it.

As a biker I want a box for my bike so that I can carry my wallet in a box on my bike.

As a holistic doctor I want a container so that I can store essential oils. 

As an Etsy seller I want cube boxes with a hinge top so that I can make music boxes to sell.

As a dumb college student I want a box with fingers so that I can easily put the box together.

As a dog I want an easily opened box so that I can access treats.

As a box I want a box so that I can not be lonely.
